content: I have discord and reach but I can't find responses to things like the swift boating of Walz.

Hi there! I'm not sure what swift boating even is, but stuff like this is usually a lost cause. We're focused primarily on independents and swing voters. That said, our Online Engagement does do some combatting misinformation work so you might sign up for a training for that. 

https://events.democrats.org/event/615101/
Swift boating is a reference to attacks on John Kerry’s service in 2004. Veterans came out and said he was lying. He really didn’t push back on it like he should’ve.
Sure thing Ophelia. I remember it well. It was disgraceful.
